#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Pāsādakampanavagga"
msgstr "2. Shaking the Stilt Longhouse"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Bhikkhusutta"
msgstr "18. A Mendicant"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.18:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā bhikkhu āsavānaṃ "
"khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power, "
"a mendicant realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.276"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.18:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.18:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.18:2.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.18:2.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.18:2.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.18:2.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme "
"sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"By developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power, a mendicant "
"realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very "
"life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to the "
"ending of defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.18:2.7"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
